    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 触发指令设置 ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            252,
            482,
            440,
            503
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设置 $\\twoheadrightarrow$ 通讯设置 $\\twoheadrightarrow$ 自定义命令 里面设置与OEM软件之间通讯，如下图：",
        "bbox": [
            273,
            517,
            852,
            576
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/b300b4345aaf050830d8ccf239494e53b66144346c4bb9afc9f2856b2479cac3.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            213,
            586,
            917,
            815
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "自定义命令分三种：",
        "bbox": [
            215,
            834,
            420,
            855
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 默认模式。OEM 发送“TRIGGER ON”扫码枪软件无需操作，如下图：",
        "bbox": [
            357,
            862,
            850,
            899
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/85acf4662d839f5d9f254f6c470d1a3ed0dfe8d672596b1f0604bcd26e71d14f.jpg",
        "image_caption": [
            "自定义命令"
        ],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            289,
            102,
            963,
            258
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2．默认“+”“-”模式。OEM发送命令“+”“-” 扫码枪软件需勾选，如下图：",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            269,
            848,
            307
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/9219146adbee8988ec25b04960de9e101d0f3a4737f742240c8db60125f7a487.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            147,
            350,
            825,
            633
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "3．自定义模式。OEM 发送特定字符命令，扫码枪软件需修改。例如发送“TRIGGER”如下图：",
        "bbox": [
            152,
            659,
            848,
            695
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/bbc3cf2d727bc53ce530f8185db3a9e517fda51e3802bb4529bb434c5ca24f3b.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            147,
            86,
            843,
            285
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2.扫码失败返回设置 ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            23,
            321,
            247,
            345
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设置 $\\twoheadrightarrow$ 系统设置 里面设置，如果扫码枪没有解到码，反馈给 OEM的信号，如下图：",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            370,
            853,
            429
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/8a33532cae579aa589b744c1075f3be363adea789309a5f67849ebf90478631d.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            147,
            439,
            848,
            821
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注意：通讯指令与反馈指令都是根据 OEM 软件里写的得来，一定要相同一致。",
        "bbox": [
            248,
            834,
            853,
            893
