        "bbox": [
            136,
            79,
            847,
            438
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4.1.自动配置调试部分。",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            13,
            446,
            290,
            467
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": ".如果配置中还有多个setup，需要将需要调试的启用其它的不启用.或者点击设置-启用的读取设置-下拉选选择需要调试的设置",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            473,
            764,
            505
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/4034da8ae8513649e00ba3f6212345e4a7ca643f1353d1f96ee5899c81a35869.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            142,
            511,
            842,
            690
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": ".点击调谐按钮右侧下拉选项只将以下4个选项打勾",
        "bbox": [
            31,
            691,
            480,
            707
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/cf11dd706d1c3e7b0734338c10112c3151ec17eba43f1d54ed1d667e7ee2b2e8.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            137,
            707,
            702,
            801
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": ".查看当前setup是否被训练如果下框显示为未训练代码五个字则当前setup被训练",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            802,
            778,
            820
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/b76888dcb1fc04fdb35051ffb326c47c82fe1db116b08b4eb5cd8f00b1b00cfe.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            95,
            821,
            845,
            899
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": ".点击取消变为训练代码四个字即可 ",
        "bbox": [
            75,
            902,
            391,
            920
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/1570dadb890d8c8f11ea7c14e9fce3f8b98ebd222278fe336bd9e42c43e90731.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            107,
            922,
            800,
            996
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": ".直接点击快速设置界面的调谐按钮：",
