        "type": "text",
        "text": ".调谐完成后如果出现多个结果，选择认为不错的配置点击-应用选定的-完成参数修改",
        "bbox": [
            16,
            388,
            386,
            435
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/f460e3746de36c7f6d1fb42436fcaa1142f78f190288e2b927de65b721ff01a7.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            418,
            321,
            991,
            592
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "4.2.手动配置调试部分",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            13,
            580,
            273,
            603
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/ce50c79da9ccdbe9968bf1ef427fbc2007bda47a5ba5d1138dfc4db1b3fb9885.jpg",
